DTN Reference Implementation
============================

Directory Structure
-------------------

applib/			dtn interface library
apps/			example dtn applications
doc/			documentation
daemon/			bundle daemon sources
ideas/			temporary code idea repository
servlib/		dtn router internals
servlib/cmd/		command interface
servlib/conv_layers/	convergence layers
servlib/debug/		debugging support code
servlib/io/		I/O and networking support code
servlib/routing/	bundle forwarding and routing logic
servlib/storage/	persistent storage management
servlib/thread/		thread / lock support implementation
servlib/util/		miscellaneous utility classes

Requirements
------------

gcc/g++ version 3.3+
pthread
tcl8.3+
tcllib
tclreadline

(one or more of the following:)
BerkeleyDB
mysql
postgresql
